The paper deals with secure inference using neural networks, which involves both cryptography and machine learning. Therefore, cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are the most likely categories. The paper also involves computer vision (cs.CV) and system engineering (cs.SY) aspects, as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques such as neural architecture search.
